### Pitch Smasher — API demo (VS Code REST Client / similar)
@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000
@token = {{signin.response.body.access_token}}

### Health (no auth)
GET {{baseUrl}}/health

### Sign up
# @name signup
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/signup
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "kamal@example.com",
  "password": "testpassword123"
}

### Sign in
# @name signin
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/signin
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "kamal@example.com",
  "password": "testpassword123"
}

### Me
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/me
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Capture idea
# @name capture
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/capture
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "transcript": "I want to build an AI tutor for rural students in Sri Lanka that works offline in Sinhala and Tamil."
}

### Scan market
# @name scan
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/scan
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "sessionId": "{{capture.response.body.sessionId}}"
}

### Audit risks
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/audit
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "sessionId": "{{capture.response.body.sessionId}}"
}

### Refine — start interview
# @name refineStart
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/refine/start
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "sessionId": "{{capture.response.body.sessionId}}"
}

### Refine — answer Q1
# @name refineA1
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/refine/answer
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "sessionId": "{{capture.response.body.sessionId}}",
  "questionIndex": 0,
  "answerTranscript": "Rural secondary students and parents who cannot afford private tutoring."
}

### Refine — answer Q2
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/refine/answer
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "sessionId": "{{capture.response.body.sessionId}}",
  "questionIndex": 1,
  "answerTranscript": "Freemium subscription at $3 per month plus school bulk licenses."
}

### Refine — answer Q3
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/refine/answer
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "sessionId": "{{capture.response.body.sessionId}}",
  "questionIndex": 2,
  "answerTranscript": "Localized offline curriculum and school partnerships."
}

### Refine — answer Q4
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/refine/answer
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "sessionId": "{{capture.response.body.sessionId}}",
  "questionIndex": 3,
  "answerTranscript": "School pilot programs and parent referral networks."
}

### Refine — answer Q5 (last)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/refine/answer
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "sessionId": "{{capture.response.body.sessionId}}",
  "questionIndex": 4,
  "answerTranscript": "I have 10 years experience in Sri Lankan education."
}

### Refine — complete
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/refine/complete
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "sessionId": "{{capture.response.body.sessionId}}"
}

### Validate
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/validate
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "sessionId": "{{capture.response.body.sessionId}}"
}

### Pitch (async job)
# @name pitch
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/pitch
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "sessionId": "{{capture.response.body.sessionId}}"
}

### Poll pitch job
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/jobs/{{pitch.response.body.jobId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get session
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/session/{{capture.response.body.sessionId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Download pitch deck (PowerPoint)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/session/{{capture.response.body.sessionId}}/export/pptx
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Download pitch deck PPTX (cached URL, JSON)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/session/{{capture.response.body.sessionId}}/export/pptx?json=1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Campaign (async)
# @name campaign
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/campaign
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "description": "Sustainable clothing brand for young professionals",
  "tone": "professional"
}

### Poll campaign job
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/jobs/{{campaign.response.body.jobId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Download campaign ZIP
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/campaign/{{campaign.response.body.campaignId}}/download
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
